[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 180     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m     // header containing patient info, study info, and acquisition parameters.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // Parse the DICOM structure to extract pixel data and metadata.
