[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // (patient info, acquisition parameters, modality type, etc.)
[0m[49m[39m  181, 165[0m:[39m[49m     dicom_object = parse DICOM from dicom_bytes
